WASHINGTON -LRB- CNN -RRB- -- The Senate Judiciary Committee will begin Judge Sonia Sotomayor 's confirmation hearings for the U.S. Supreme Court on July 13 , the committee 's chairman , Sen. Patrick Leahy of Vermont , said Tuesday .

